name: Audi Q7
description: Audi Q7 is a good luxury midsize SUV . On the performance front, the Q7 impresses with its array of turbocharged engines and its fusion of a pillow-soft ride with engaging handling and nimble steering.

name: Mercedes Benz
description: Mercedes-Benz produces consumer luxury vehicles and commercial vehicles. Its first Mercedes-Benz-badged vehicles were produced in 1926. In 2018, Mercedes-Benz was the largest seller of premium vehicles in the world, having sold 2.31 million passenger cars.

name: BMW X7
description: The 2022 BMW X7 is a seven-passenger three-row SUV that is available in two trim levels: xDrive40i and M50i. The xDrive40i is powered by a turbocharged 3.0-liter inline-six cylinder engine good for 335 horsepower and 331 lb-ft of torque

name: Audi A6
description: The 2023 A6 is the quintessential Audi luxury sedan, featuring a cabin stuffed with technology that's expertly put together using premium materials.
